trans_title: 滚石杂志编辑部的故事
introduction: Follow six young writers with the opportunity of a lifetime -- a summer working as writers for Rolling Stone in New York City. They'll fight over assignments, struggle to land celebrity interviews and race against deadlines... all in hopes of seeing their words and byline in the pages of the legendary music magazine.Find out who has the "write stuff" to win a coveted staff writer's position, and the right to say, "I'm from Rolling Stone."
